{"tid":2252182,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"翠雅山房闢作隔離營 工程師堵路示威被控 今控方撤控簽保守行為","createTime":"2020-10-21T09:58:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T10:12:01.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e98c8979fb27df94b0470ad45302cb4f2197efa1","tid":2252182,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T09:58:56.000Z","msg":"今年2月食物及衞生局徵用美孚饒宗頤文化館翠雅山房作武漢肺炎隔離營，遭過千名美孚街坊遊行反對，有人以雜物堵路，警方事後以在公眾地方造成阻礙罪拘控四人，其中兩人另於被捕時涉打到警員臉部，被控襲警罪。案件今於九龍城法院再訊時，控方同意對其中被控堵路的工程師撤控，改以簽保守行為方式處理。裁判官張天雁下令該工程師自簽800元、守行為一年，其間不得干犯同類型罪行。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">案情指案發當日有「暴動者」於美孚區出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，抗議政府徵用附近旅館作新冠肺炎抗疫中心。有便衣警員在荔枝角道馬路喬裝成旁觀者，其間看見第三被告連同他人衝出馬路，又扔垃圾袋於路上。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201021/PMLA74QEZFC6JIM5YBO67UIIGU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201021%2FPMLA74QEZFC6JIM5YBO67UIIGU%2F&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPedgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=5ad77f61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201021%2FPMLA74QEZFC6JIM5YBO67UIIGU%2F&h=c7512a18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201021/PMLA74QEZFC6JIM5YBO67UIIGU/</a>"},{"pid":"899b50801c51cb1d12f020299c1e7de72eb5dbdd","tid":2252182,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T10:00:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"028204bb9fc6bf04b67066ba21ae17ad76a73d49","tid":2252182,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"899b50801c51cb1d12f020299c1e7de72eb5dbdd","tid":2252182,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"